{"id":9042,"date":"2024-01-12T17:12:15","date_gmt":"2020-05-12T11:42:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=9042"},"modified":"2023-04-15T15:09:27","modified_gmt":"2023-04-15T09:39:27","slug":"kitchen-pantry-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-pantry-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Stock In Style! Latest Kitchen Pantry Design Ideas For Your Home!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>If you are deeply passionate about feasting, cooking and inviting guests over, a well-designed pantry in your home is an absolute must. Explore these latest kitchen pantry design ideas and pick your favourite one.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most Indian homes do not have a dedicated kitchen pantry and homeowners often store groceries in large containers or <em>dabbas,<\/em> as they are commonly known as,&nbsp; openly on shelves or inside cabinets. While this still works it is often unsightly and hard to find things when you&#8217;re in the midst of cooking or when you have friends\/family helping you out in the kitchen. A kitchen pantry is therefore, an elegant solution to stow away all your non-perishable groceries.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Old and traditional homes boast of grand walk-in pantries and are quite reflective of the utilitarian aspect of pantries. While modern day home layouts are not designed with a dedicated space to house a kitchen pantry there are various designs to re-implement this timeless necessity. From the classic floor-to-ceiling pantry designs to modern standalone pantry units &#8211; the designs of today keep in mind the requirements of busy urban households.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern pantry designs make smart use of dead spaces while more extravagant ones are built as an extension of the kitchen itself. Here are a handful of clever kitchen pantry design ideas for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Secret Stash For Your Midnight Snacks!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re tight on space in your kitchen then this design is for you! Take a look around your home and find all dead corners or spaces &#8211; here is where you can make smart use of it with clever design. In this image a dead space under the staircase has been transformed into a clever pull out pantry design. This pantry design is an excellent idea for small apartments. You can store your groceries, dry food items and snacks. This design hides everything away when not in use. One side of this pantry is designed with open shelves where you can display your cookbooks or potted plants toup the style quotient of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165408\/kitchen-pantry-design-under-staircase.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen pantry design with a dead space under the staircase transformed into a clever pull out kitchen pantry design\" class=\"wp-image-9045\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165408\/kitchen-pantry-design-under-staircase.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165408\/kitchen-pantry-design-under-staircase-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165408\/kitchen-pantry-design-under-staircase-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165408\/kitchen-pantry-design-under-staircase-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/under-stairs-storage-ideas-for-small-spaces\/\">Under Stairs Storage Design Ideas for Small Spaces<\/a> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Cool kitchen design hacks on a budget\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/17140431\/cool-kitchen-design-hacks-on-budget.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Away From Prying Eyes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to hide your edibles but still want easy access to them when you cook then design a cabinet pantry like this in your kitchen. When shut, all you will see is a chalkboard finish with doodles or quotes if you wish to bring in some artwork! This pantry design is tall enough to store all your condiments, snacks and spices keeping your countertop clutter-free and your kitchen organised.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165305\/kitchen-pantry-cabinet-design.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen pantry design using cabinet pantry to make useful kitchen pantry design images\" class=\"wp-image-9043\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165305\/kitchen-pantry-cabinet-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165305\/kitchen-pantry-cabinet-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165305\/kitchen-pantry-cabinet-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165305\/kitchen-pantry-cabinet-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Walk-In Kitchen Pantry Design For Large Homes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As the world is under a pandemic trap what is everyone most worried about? Yes, stocking food and groceries. But where do you store your stashes of panic buying? In a walk-in pantry! Here in this image a portion of this kitchen is separated with the glass door that makes this a walk-in pantry. Ample cabinets, shelves and a dado wall offer enough space to store all your groceries, staples, utensils. Just shut the door when not in use. And if you have a large home, this is your go-to design!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165512\/walk-in-kitchen-pantry-design-large-homes.jpg\" alt=\"Walk-in kitchen pantry design for large home to store all your groceries, staples, utensils\" class=\"wp-image-9047\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165512\/walk-in-kitchen-pantry-design-large-homes.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165512\/walk-in-kitchen-pantry-design-large-homes-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165512\/walk-in-kitchen-pantry-design-large-homes-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165512\/walk-in-kitchen-pantry-design-large-homes-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Travel Back In Time With This Pantry Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Doesn&#8217;t this pantry design take you back to the old-school bakeries or book shops? It is a timeless classic. If you are blessed with an extra room or planning to divide your kitchen to create a small walk-in pantry for yourself opt for this old school look. It adds a serious amount of class and functionality to any simple pantry design. As shown in this image, this elegant white kitchen pantry has everything you need &#8211; style and utility. Besides, it is designed with ample storage options to store all your edibles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165447\/pantry-cupboard-designs-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Pantry cupboard designs kitchen to make a simple kitchen pantry design\" class=\"wp-image-9046\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165447\/pantry-cupboard-designs-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165447\/pantry-cupboard-designs-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165447\/pantry-cupboard-designs-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165447\/pantry-cupboard-designs-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add Some Sunshine<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A small space is an excellent excuse to use a bold colour. However, you must ensure you choose a colour scheme that blends with the colour story of the rest of the room\u2019s interiors. This yellow painted kitchen pantry reminds us of a sunny day in spring! It blends in well with the dining room set-up makes the space look bright and chirpy. This simple pantry is designed in a small space between the kitchen and dining room where the walls are wallpapered in beige and white. This cheerful yellow pantry grabs all the attention. It is designed as an open-display setup and has a series of open boxed racks and drawers to store your groceries and greens.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165535\/yellow-kitchen-pantry-design.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen pantry design with yellow painted kitchen pantry to store groceries and greens\" class=\"wp-image-9048\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165535\/yellow-kitchen-pantry-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165535\/yellow-kitchen-pantry-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165535\/yellow-kitchen-pantry-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/12165535\/yellow-kitchen-pantry-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Modular kitchen interior for a hassle free cooking experience\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/15145454\/modular-kitchen-interior-for-hassle-free-cooking-experience.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The ideal kitchen pantry lets you organise everything in the most optimal manner with ample storage and unlimited shelf space to store your culinary items. Whether you&#8217;re looking for a full-scale walk-in kitchen pantry or more space-calculated cabinet kitchen pantry design, these modern ideas get new-age homeowners to move and cook with the times. Let us know which one is your favourite in the comments below!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">Modular Kitchen Designs By DesignCafe<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/10-different-types-of-kitchen-countertops\/\">10 Different Types Of Kitchen Countertops<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/maximize-storage-space-in-your-modular-kitchen\/\">How to Maximise Storage Space in Your Modular Kitchen<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <d